Source: typos
Section: misc
Maintainer: Local Builder <builder@localhost>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), curl
Homepage: https://github.com/crate-ci/typos

Package: typos
Architecture: amd64
Description: Source code spell checker.
 typos is a source code spell checker that finds and corrects common
 typos in source code, filenames, and documentation. It is fast,
 low false-positive, and designed for use in CI pipelines.
